  <brief_title>Dose Finding Study to Assess Safety and Efficacy of Stem Cells in Liver Cirrhosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Parallel Group Randomized Open Blinded End Point Evaluation, Multicentric, Dose Escalation, Phase -II Study Assessing the Safety and Efficacy of Intraarterial (Hepatic) Ex-vivo Cultured Adult Allogenic Mesenchymal Stem Cells in Patients With Alcoholic Liver Cirrhosis</official_title>
