  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate the safety and efficacy of mesenchymal stem cells in patients with
      cirrhosis of liver. Stem cells will be injected into the hepatic artery. Improvement in
      various parameters will be observed over 2 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
